       <div class="well">
        <h2 class="widgettitle">
         About
        </h2>
        Persis Drell is Stanford's thirteenth provost. As the chief academic and chief budgetary officer of the university, the provost is responsible for administering the academic program, including both instruction and research, and for the alignment of the administrative and support functions of the university with its academic purposes.
        <p>
         <a class="more-link" href="/about-the-provost">
          <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right">
          </i>
          <span>
           More about Provost Drell
          </span>
         </a>
        </p>
       </div>
